The goblin kitchen key is a quest item in the Observatory Quest. It found in a chest in the Observatory Dungeon and is used to open the Kitchen gate in the same dungeon. The chest in which the key is found is different for every player, but remains the same once found. Attempting to obtain another from the chest while one is in the inventory yields the message: Another one will be of little use. However, it is possible to obtain duplicates if it is banked. It can be reobtained after the quest.

It cannot be added to the key ring.
